data.description: THIS BEAUTIFUL  5 bedroom 3 bath home sitting on 3195 hsf. The home includes an upstairs family room, 9ft ceilings, stainless steel appliance package, professionally landscaped and sodded yard, and fully finished garage with door openers. This home is located in Columbia's County Hidden Creek subdivision; in Grovetown, GA. Hidden Creek is in walking distances to Columbia County Bakers Elementary, Columbia Middle, and Grovetown High school. Hidden Creek is also an amenity community that includes a nature trail, playground, clubhouse, and a Jr. Olympic Pool. Also is close to shopping centers and parks.
